mechanism that in-network devices use to limit the ability of end<br>
users to discover services. A deviation which accomplishes a similar<br>
objective, though may be seen as different from a freedom of<br>
expression perspective, is the injection of incorrect responses to<br>
queries.=C2=A0 The most prominent example of this behavior occurs in China,=
