where requests for lookups of sites which have been deemed<br>
inappropriate will trigger the network to respond with a bogus<br>
response, causing the client to ignore the real response when it<br>
subsequently arrives. Unlike the other forms of discussion discussed<br>
above, injection does not stifle the ability of a server to announce<br>
