https://mailarchive.ietf.org/arch/attach/hrpc/pdfbyB1Dp.pdf
- - Discussion of Methodology draft  (20 min)
		Cases
			IP
			DNS
			HTTP
			P2P
			XMPP
			VPN
		Definitions
		Way forward
- - Discussion of Glossary draft	(10 min)
- - Discussion of Guidelines draft (20 min)
- - Open discussion other drafts, papers, ideas (20 min)
- - Charter update status &c. (if necessary - 5 Min)
- - Next steps (5 min)
- - AOB

I would very much like to invite other topics and presentations to be
part of the agenda (perhaps the draft by Mark, or further work by the
research group of Roland Bless).

I'm very much looking forward to your ideas and suggestions.

Best,

Niels



