--- abstract<br>
<br>
This document present an overview of the project to map engineering<br>
concepts at the protocol level that may be related to promotion and<br>
protection of the freedom of expression and association.<br>
<br>
This first draft is intended to provide the framework for reporting on<br>
the study, initial results and basic considerations. At a later stage it<br=
>
will fold in the work being done in the Methodology and Glossary drafts<br>
as well as the work being done in the case studies. It also folds in<br>
some of the text included in the original proposal for the HRPC.<br>
<br>
Discussion on this draft at: <a href=3D"mailto:hrpc@irtf.org">hrpc@irtf.org=
</a> //<br>
<a href=3D"https://www.irtf.org/mailman/admindb/hrpc" rel=3D"noreferrer" ta=
rget=3D"_blank">https://www.irtf.org/mailman/admindb/hrpc</a><br>
